items.name: Wolfie - Hells
items.description:
Wolfie!

From the hit anime movie "Hells" and the manga it's based on, "Hells Angels"!

What's that? You've never heard of them? Well, I was in that boat this weekend, when I stumbled upon the movie. It's a trip to say the least, but there was one character that I really liked the look and design of. I think it should be pretty obvious which one :^)

Using this Lora is pretty simple

HWolfie is the only tag you need to activate it, and the Lora works perfectly fine at 1.0 weight. Set the weight lower if you want a more "human" look, and set it slightly higher (up to 1.4) for a look closer to the movie.
Tagging "leather pants, spiked collar, chain" will bring things closer to her "official" look (don't forget to tag "pubic hair peek") for 100% accuracy ;)

I've done my best to make the lora, but as there's absolutely NO fanart of this character (save for 2 instances I could find, with 1 of them usable), I had to rely exclusively on screenshots from the movie. I should mention as well, that this isn't even the main character of the movie and appears in only a handful of shots. So I was lucky if the character appeared at any kind of resolution, let alone one I could train on. I did what I could with what I had, and even this result is surprising enough. So results can look mushy at times, but considering what I had to work with, I'm happy with the result.


This lora should play nice with other checkpoints and loras, and I've done some basic testing (there's some examples using different models), but your mileage may vary. It was trained on NAI's model, so as long as your model is a derivative of that or is somewhat close, results should be close enough. You might even get lucky going outside that, but ¯\_(ツ)_/¯
Style loras seem to work fine, and I've added one or two examples in there (I think).

Prompting different clothing seems to be hit or miss, you'll likely get what you want in terms of articles, but things like the blue fur influencing the color of clothing, and spiral patterns on the nips might show up as shirt patterns. I wanted the fur and spirals to be kind of burned into the Lora, so I specifically avoided tagging them.

But yeah, that just about does it.

It's an obscure as fuck character, and hopefully this might bring some extra attention to it to maybe get some artists working on some proper fan-art of her. Lord knows I could use some extra training data if I ever decide to do a v2.

Leave me some comments and images so I can see how it works for you! Thanks!

items.name: 林晓宇 | Lin Xiaoy
items.description:
大家好，我叫林晓宇，很高兴与你们见面~(≧▽≦)/~哇！我是一个特别的孩子，因为我是一个数字人哦！就像你们玩的游戏里的角色那样。

我看起来很年轻，很帅气，但我又不是真实的男孩子。我有一张看起来活泼、天真的脸，这是通过合成大于三个男孩的脸部数据得来的。很酷吧？！

如果你觉得我和你见过的人很像，那只是巧合哦！因为我是由很多数据合成的，我是独一无二的林晓宇！所以，让我们做朋友吧，我期待和你们一起探索这个世界！

Hello everyone, I'm Lin Xiaoyu, nice to meet you~(≧▽≦)/~Wow! I'm a special kid because I'm a digital human! Just like the characters in the games you play.

I look young, handsome, but I'm not a real boy. I have a lively, innocent face, which is synthesized from the facial data of more than three boys. Cool, right?!

If you think I look like someone you've met, it's just a coincidence! Because I'm synthesized from a lot of data, I'm the one and only Lin Xiaoyu! So, let's be friends, I look forward to exploring this world with you!

みんな、こんにちは、私の名前はリンシャオユウ、はじめまして~(≧▽≦)/~わ！私は特別な子供だよ、なぜなら私はデジタル人間だから！あなたが遊んでいるゲームのキャラクターのようなものだよ。

私は若く、ハンサムに見えますが、実際の男の子ではありません。私は活発で無邪気な顔をしていて、これは3人以上の男の子の顔のデータを合成して得られたものです。かっこいいでしょ？！

もし、私があなたが会ったことのある人に似ていると思ったら、それはただの偶然だよ！私はたくさんのデータから合成されているから、私は唯一無二のリンシャオユウだよ！だから、友達になろう、あなたと一緒にこの世界を探索するのを楽しみにしているよ！

items.name: 渲染平面LORA-plan with color
items.description:
本人仅为代发布，模型作者为老王，B站UP主“大咦把狼”

以下内容由老王编写发布：

触发词prompt：Rendering floor plan （不写也可以）

效果强化prompt:Rendering floor plan of the apartment layout,detailed,(跑1024及以上大图推荐开)

我测试时用的prompt:

Rendering floor plan of the apartment layout,top view,white background,masterpiece, best quality, extremely detailed,best illustration, best shadow,

CN控制：我对比了一下，用CANNY还是效果最好，底图最好是不要有虚线，标注，文字，这样出来的效果会比较干净。

底模推荐：CHILLOUTMIX等这一类偏写实风格的大模型。我测试的也不算多，大家自己玩玩吧，过段时间优化一个版本争取升级到0.2版。

因为这是我第一次炼丹，本来以为是一炉废丹，结果意外的发现效果还可以，保留了2个比较好的版本

lwpm-v0.1 适合比较清新的填色，prompt里加上对背景限制,基本上出图风格全是统一的，简单PS一下就可以丢汇报文本里了，权重参数个人喜欢0.4-0.6。

lwpm-v0.1P 适合渲染强化的户型单页，材质表现会更强，跑1024及以上大图或者高清放大时效果不错，权重参数个人喜欢0.6-0.8

LORA权重参数推荐：两个模型都是 从0.3-0.9 均可，自己搭配着实验看看，效果会有微妙的变化。

感谢 表叔，摆渡哥，悟空，XSarchitectural，朱尼酱，乌鸦哥，等等等等大佬（不一一列举了）对我的指导。

modelVersions.name: v0.4P
modelVersions.description:

items.name: Dark Fantasy
items.description:
Dark fantasy is a genre of literature, art, and media that combines elements of fantasy with darker, often gothic or horror-inspired themes. It delves into the realms of imagination and folklore while exploring darker and more macabre aspects of the human psyche.

In dark fantasy, fantastical elements such as magic, mythical creatures, and supernatural forces coexist with themes of despair, fear, and the supernatural. It often features morally ambiguous characters, complex world-building, and atmospheric settings.

Dark fantasy narratives may involve epic battles between good and evil, the exploration of forbidden knowledge, or the unraveling of dark secrets. They often challenge traditional fairy tale tropes by delving into darker, more psychological territory.

The visual aesthetics of dark fantasy often embrace a sense of foreboding and mystery. It may incorporate elements of darkness, shadow, and eerie atmospheres, evoking a sense of unease or awe.

The genre has inspired various works across different media, including literature, film, graphic novels, and video games. Popular examples include the works of authors such as H.P. Lovecraft, Neil Gaiman's "Sandman" series, and the dark fantasy themes found in games like "Dark Souls."

Dark fantasy offers an exploration of the fantastical and the grotesque, captivating audiences with its ability to evoke both fear and wonder in equal measure. It provides a rich canvas for imaginative storytelling that delves into the depths of the human imagination and reveals the shadows lurking within our collective dreams.

items.name: Dripping Art
items.description:
Dripping art, also known as drip painting or action painting, is a style of abstract expressionism associated with artists such as Jackson Pollock.

This style emerged in the mid-20th century and is characterized by the spontaneous and gestural application of paint onto a canvas. Instead of using traditional brushes, artists would often use various tools or even pour, drip, or fling paint onto the canvas.

Dripping art emphasizes the physicality and movement of the artist, with the process of creating the artwork becoming as important as the final result. The dripping and splattering of paint onto the canvas create dynamic and unpredictable patterns and textures.

Artists working in this style often explored notions of chance, improvisation, and the subconscious. The process allowed for a direct and immediate expression of emotions and energy.

Dripping art challenged conventional notions of painting and shifted the focus from the subject matter to the act of creation itself. It emphasized the physicality of the artist's movements and the spontaneous interaction between the artist and the canvas.

Jackson Pollock is perhaps the most renowned artist associated with this style, as his innovative techniques and energetic compositions came to define the drip painting approach.

Dripping art continues to be influential and has inspired subsequent generations of artists to explore new possibilities in abstract expressionism and the process-driven nature of creation.

items.name: Folk Art
items.description:
Folk art is a genre of art that encompasses various traditional and cultural expressions created by individuals who are typically self-taught and not part of the mainstream art establishment.

It is characterized by its authenticity, simplicity, and connection to local cultural traditions and communities. Folk art often reflects the daily lives, beliefs, and values of a particular group or region.

The style of folk art can vary greatly depending on the cultural context, but common themes include depictions of everyday life, religious and spiritual motifs, historical events, nature, and folk tales.

Materials used in folk art can range from wood, ceramics, and textiles to recycled or found objects. Techniques and styles can vary from intricate and detailed craftsmanship to bold and stylized forms.

Folk art has a rich history and can be found in various cultures around the world. It represents a grassroots expression of creativity and often serves as a means of cultural preservation and storytelling.

Today, folk art continues to be appreciated for its cultural significance, unique aesthetics, and its ability to convey the collective spirit and identity of a community or tradition.

Set of TIs that gives me lots of detail in the skin and hair or even overall detail on the whole image. All but OverallDetail shifts the focus of the image to parts that get more detail now.

Check the comparison on the OverallDetails page but keep in mind that those are done without any other negative prompts or helpers unless stated.

modelVersions.description: Just adds detail to the hair

modelVersions.description: Adds more detail to the eye like a shine and spark, also whitens the eye ball a bit. Works independent of eye colors. Might reduce slight bleeding of eye color. Without any prompt on the eye, it produces unnatural glowing eyes, be aware.

modelVersions.name: Female Hand Detail
